reviews.review_text: vg rec, vg show vg recording that may benefit from a bit of eq (but is inherently very strong). The show is wonderful as well. A few moments where things slip off the rails. But it's just filled with potent energy and some gorgeous playing.
great Black Muddy River Jerry just does a great job with this song, and the set list for set IIA is interesting and has good flow, check it out!
